articles.title: How Larry Ellison Became the World’s Second-Richest Person - Bloomberg.com
articles.description: Larry Ellison dropped out of college before co-founding what eventually grew into one of the world’s biggest technology companies: Oracle Corp. The fortune he amassed propelled him to the ranks of the uber-rich.
